snippet.title: Match Highlights - Brazil 4:1 South Korea - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
Brazil stormed into the quarterfinals of the #FIFAWorldCup for a record 17th time after beating South Korea 4-1 at Stadium 974.

The five-time champions stormed to a four-goal lead in the first half through goals from Vinicius Jr, Neymar, Richarlison & Lucas Paqueta.

Tite's side took the foot off the gas in the second half to see out the match. Paik Seung-ho pulled one back for the Asian side with a long-range effort and that was to be the only goal in the final 45 minutes.

Brazil will now face Croatia in the quarter-final on Dec 9, 8:30 pm.

Lyrics -

Chhori tedhi tedhi taak ke,
Likdi saare mauke naap ke,
Chhora ke khanjar ghaal ke,
Beran dar ja kade ram te,

Chhori tedhi tedhi taak ke,
Likdi saare mauke naap ke,
Chhora ke khanjar ghaal ke,
Beran dar ja kade ram te,

Chhori Ghani syaani ghani syaani ghani syaani,
Chhore mar gaye mar gaye mar gaye haan bin maange paani,

Nakhro, dekha pahli dafa,
College ke bahar dass kya thi raza,
Chale left to right bata kyu di saza,
Louis, LV tight teri kaidi ada,
Chhore paache paache haande leke landi jeep,
Tere chakkar me kare kaand galt hi cheej,
Gere 5 inch heel, Chhore leve poori feel,
Tere bhaav bhi to fly kare poori dheel,

Makke tip to toe tu poori gach hai,
26 ki kamar poori lachke,
21 ki umar, kya ye sach hai?
Mere bethi hai nishaane pe rah bachke,

Halla mach gaya poore gaam me,
Ib bethak laage shaam ne,
Chhora ke khanjar ghaal ke,
Beran darja kadi raam te,

Chhori Ghani syaani ghani syaani ghani syaani,
Chhore mar gaye mar gaye mar gaye haan bin maange paani,

Tu hoga badmaash tere laake me chhore,
Tere jaise pade fail mere khaate me chhore,
Manne Jhaanse me laane ki koshish na kar,
Maanja padega ghane ghaate me chhore,

Teri chikni chupdi baat me,
Chhori aati koni saath me,
Chhora ke khanjar ghaal ke,
Kyunkar darjua raam te,

Haan me ghani syaani ghani syaani ghani syaani,
Chhore mar gaye mar gaye mar gaye haan bin maange paani


#GhaniSyaani #MCSquare #ShehnaazGill

snippet.title: Match Highlights - Argentina 2:1 Australia - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
Argentina booked their place in the last eight for the 10th time in #FIFAWorldCup history, edging Australia 2-1 at the Ahmad bin Ali Stadium.

Lionel Messi, who hadn't scored in the knockout stages of the competition, opened the scoring in the 35th minute. Julian Alvarez doubled the lead for Lionel Scaloni's side after making the most of an error by Socceroos goalkeeper Mathew Ryan.

Australia pulled one back through an unfortunate own goal by Enzo Fernandez. But Argentina held their nerve to make it through.

snippet.title: FRENCH FRIES | Crispy French Fried potatoes Recipe Cooking In Village | Finger Chips | Easy Snacks
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook a French Fried Potato recipe. This French Fries recipe is a simple and easy snack recipe that everyone can cook quickly at home. We first boiled the sliced potatoes, then we sun dried them to make crispy Frech Fries.

Finally, we eat this snack in the evening by adding some hand-ground species masalas. Yummy and Crispy.

Dhyan Sreenivasan is an Indian actor, and film director who works in Malayalam films. Dhyan Sreenivasan made his acting debut with Thira, directed by Dhyan Sreenivasan elder brother Vineeth Sreenivasan. Dhyan is the younger son of noted actor and screenwriter Sreenivasan. Dhyan Sreenivasan brother Vineeth Sreenivasan is a singer, actor and director who also works in Malayalam cinema. Dhyan married his longtime girlfriend Arpita Sebastian on 7 April 2017. He made his film debut with the Malayalam film Thira which has Shobana in main lead role. In the film, Dhyan Sreenivasan did a supporting role along with two-time National Award winning actress Shobana. His performance in the film was generally well-received by critics and the audience.

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Saradaaga || A Family Picnic || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Saradaaga || A Family Picnic || MCM

In this new saradaga episode of Middle Class Madhu, a funny discussion starts between 1A Master and his wife Bhagyam. The discussion later turns into a serious plan when Bhagyam asks him to plan a picnic with the colony. She motivates 1A Master to be the mastermind behind the picnic plan while they portray the plan being executed by Sarada Subbarao. Finally, after convincing sarada Subba Rao, the picnic plan gets started. In surprise, Budatha invites his girlfriend Geetha to the picnic. Seeing Geetha madhu surprises him and he tries to put a fight between Geetha and Budatha, but his plan turns out to be profitable for Budatha. Everybody enjoys the places in Vizag, and Madhu, with his Naatu Guntala Gang, starts funny plans to make the picnic even more funnier. 1A master who is so excited and looking happy in the picnic was the target for Madhu and His Gang. Watch out for this fun-filled episode, Saradaga! And we promise you a 30-minute fun ride.

Farq Episode 11 - [Eng Sub]- Faysal Quraishi - Sehar Khan - Adeel Chaudhry - 5th December 2022 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

Explore the new Island, get around with the Dirt Bike, use newly forged weapons like the Shockwave Hammer and Ex-Caliber Rifle, discover Augments, and so much more

The Citadel

This point of interest is the castle of The Ageless, whose duty protects Reality.

Shattered Slabs

The Quarry is the site of a large Kinetic Ore mining operation. Use Kinetic Ore for physics sorcery:

Brutal Bastion

This headquarters of the Reality Warriors is located atop a snowy mountain. Speaking of snow, hit snow with your Pickaxe to create a snowball, jump inside the snowball, then get rolling. You can attack enemies this way too‚Ä¶

Slappy Shores

The Industrial Town is most known as the location of the ‚ÄúSlap Juice‚Äù factory. 

In addition to new locations to explore, discover new ways to get around.

Steer Your Dirt Bike Steed

One of the many ways to get to these places? The trusty, two-wheel Trail Thrasher. Pull off tricks on this dirt bike and use weapons as you ride.

Switch up your playstyle with Augments.

At intervals in your match, you‚Äôll be given a randomized choice of ‚ÄúReality Augments.‚Äù The longer you remain in the match, the more Reality Augments you‚Äôll have stacked. Your Reality Augments last until the end of the match.

Jump into Chapter 4 now!

snippet.description:
England created history on day 1 of the first Test match by scoring the most runs on an opening day. England batters were simply brilliant as they came with the right intent against Pakistan and smashed the bowlers all over the park. England ended Day 1 on high as Zak Crawley, Ben Duckett, Ollie Pope and Harry Brook scored centuries for England to post a mammoth total of 506 runs on board.

snippet.description:
"Resham Ka Rumal" has always been a song to sway your legs. Bringing a modern and uplifting rendition with lyrics penned by Rajesh Manthan and a modern mood by Gourov Dasgupta. Sung by Shruti Rane and featuring none other than Divya Agarwal. The video is directed and choreographed by Prince Gupta.

Featuring: Divya Agarwal
Director & Choreographer ‚Äì Prince Gupta
Singer- Shruti Rane
D.O.P. ‚Äì Ajay Pandey
Stylist- Jimmy Z
Music ‚Äì Gourov Dasgupta  
Programmed, mixed and mastered ‚Äì Som Riggs

Asst. editor - Ulleses Correia 
Production house ‚Äì Prince Gupta Films

Divya‚Äôs Team:

Assistant - Nirmal Shah and Akshay

Prince Gupta Film Team: Kamal Singh Bathi , Durgesh Sambariya, Vishal Vedre, Saiprasad Amare , Sujit 

Original Credits:
Original Music Director: Ila Arun, Lalit Sen
Original Singer: Ila Arun
Original Lyrics: Ila Arun

Lyrics:
Dum dum damke jhumka mera, maarda lashkaara,

Rang birangi odhni main, odh aayi yaara,

Sun zara bole kya dil ka iktara..

Resham ka.. haan
Resham ka roomal gale mein daal ke,  tu aaja na.. aa wait karoon main, 

Main cherry wali lipistick lagake, arey.. kab se khadi hoon darwajje pe..

Resham ka.... haan

Meri nathani haale dole, mera bichhua chham bole, Re ,

Meri nathani haale dole, mera bichhua chham chham bole..

Meri laal chunariya, sar se sarakati jaaye

Dildaar mere main, haan branded wala perfume lagaake are, kab se chhupi hoon mai rajaayi mein, o o

Resham ka.. Haan

Jab jab dekhoon chehra tera,
Hosh huye aawaara
Bajaran teri huyi main,
Tu mera banjaara,

Dholna  sabse tu mujhko hai pyaara,

Resham ka...
Resham ka roomal gale mein daalke tu aa jaana, darling mere main,. Main mehngi waali goggle lagake yaham  kab se khadi hoon darwajje pe..oo

Resham ka...

Mai cherry wali lipistick lagake are
Mai mehengi wali goggle lagake aha
Han branded wala perfume lagake  

Kabse khadi hun darawajje pe,o o o
Resham Ka.. Haa

snippet.title: Hit 2 Non Spoiler Review | Adivi Sesh, Meenakshi | Sailesh Kolanu, Nani | Telugu Movies | Thyview
snippet.description:
Hello All Welcome to thyview. here is our non-spoiler review of the film Hit 2 directed by DR sailesh Kolanu.

First things first cinema choosaka naa experience cheppali ante, its engaging.decent. baane vundi.2 hours run time helped..but but but meeru usually ilanti thrillers choodaka pothe kanuka meeku khacchitham ga nacchuthundi. ala kakunda meeru naa laaga eppativo criminal minds,Mentalist, ncis, csi, castle nundi monna vacchina mind hunter, mare of eastown, Dahmer documentary daaka ilanti content consume chesunte kanuka meeda ok baane vundi and pedda thrilling ga anipinchaka poina movie end ayinappudu oka satisfaction tho theatre nundi bayataki vastharu.and meelo kontha mandhiki vunde regular questions, Hit 1 kanna bavunda ? i would say yes, this is better written ela anedi detailed ga tharuvatha cheptha.  and next question vacchesi hit2 choodali ante mundu hit1 choodala ? well choosthe konni connections artham avuthai, but choodakapoina hit2 works as a stand alone film.

snippet.title: NEW! Maddam Sir - Ep 675 - 3 Dec 2022 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 675: Maddam Sir Bani Urmila
--------------------------------------------
Haseena Mallik has been injured after falling to the ground while playing, so Karishma Singh brings a doctor to treat her. As soon as Haseena Mallik awakens she begins acting like Urmila, she catches the doctor charging a hefty fee. Karishma Singh becomes skeptical because she thinks Haseena can't be changed by a minor cut on her head. Since Santosh has left the "thana" at this point, she also openly flirts with Cheetah. Watch the episode.  
 
Show Name ‚Äì Maddam Sir
Star Cast ‚Äì  Gulki Joshi, Yukti Kapoor, Sonali Naik, Bhavika Sharma, Pankhuri Awasthy Rode, Priyanshu Singh, and Ajay Jadhav
Episode No ‚Äì 675, 3 Dec 2022
Produced By ‚Äì  Jay Mehta

#MaddamSir  #‡§Æ‡•à‡§°‡•ç‡§°‡§Æ‡§∏‡§∞ #SAB

Click here to Subscribe to SAB TV Channel: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sabtv?sub_confirmation=1

About The Show:
-----------------------------
Set in Lucknow the show is based in one such all-women Police station made by 4 beautiful quirky women. Pushpa, the oldest of them, is the head constable who tries to balance her life between home and work. Karishma, the Sub Inspector, is fish out of the water as she is at loggerheads with the philosophy of the police station. She beats before she talks but now she has to solve all cases through reconciliation. Santosh Sharma is a young new recruit and a typical lonely girl in the city. The head of the pack is S.H.O Haseena Mallik, witty, romantic leads by example. The common challenge for all these women is to bring sensitivity to their policing while dealing with cases that come to this police station. Hence their solution is most unusual. The characters and the cases add to the fun and humor of the show. While Pushpa and Karishma are the saas-bahu duo, who keep us entertained by their Squabbles, Haseena - Karishma's ideological differences add to the drama madam and comedy.
